name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: (SELECT count(1) FROM work_item WHERE IS_DELETED = '0' AND PROJECT_ID = t1.`ID`)
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: ALL_WORK_ITEMS

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: (SELECT count(1) FROM work_item WHERE IS_DELETED = '0' AND `STATE` in (select ID from work_item_state where TYPE = 'completed') AND PROJECT_ID = t1.`ID`)
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: COMPLETED_WORK_ITEMS

queryCode:
SELECT
(SELECT count(1) FROM work_item WHERE IS_DELETED = '0' AND PROJECT_ID = t1.`ID`) AS `ALL_WORK_ITEMS`,
t1.`ASSIGNEE_ID`,
t1.`ASSIGNEE_NAME`,
(SELECT count(1) FROM work_item WHERE IS_DELETED = '0' AND `STATE` in (select ID from work_item_state where TYPE = 'completed') AND PROJECT_ID = t1.`ID`) AS `COMPLETED_WORK_ITEMS`,
t1.`CREATE_MAN`,
t1.`CREATE_TIME`,
t1.`END_AT`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`IDENTIFIER`,
t1.`IS_ARCHIVED`,
t1.`IS_DELETED`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`SCOPE_ID`,
t1.`SCOPE_TYPE`,
t1.`START_AT`,
t1.`STATE`,
t1.`TYPE`,
t1.`UPDATE_MAN`,
t1.`UPDATE_TIME`,
t1.`VISIBILITY`
FROM `PROJECT` t1
